FBIS4-65056 "drweu092_b_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-092 Daily Report 12 May 1994 BENELUX Belgium Deputy Prime Minister Supports Mediation Role in Israel Deputy Prime Minister Supports Mediation Role in Israel BR1105143194 Brussels LA LIBRE BELGIQUE in French 11-12 May 94 p 5 BR1105143194 Brussels LA LIBRE BELGIQUE French BFN [Report signed R.A.G: "Israel: Visit by Elio Di Rupo -- Major Disagreements Continue With Palestinians"] [Excerpt] "Belgium should continue its mediation policy between the Israelis and Palestinians," Belgian Deputy Prime Minister Elio Di Rupo said after talks with Israeli and Palestinian leaders. Di Rupo was leading a delegation of socialist senators and regional ministers on a fact-finding mission to Israel, to the territories that are shortly to become autonomous, and Jordan. [passage omitted]
